Dogs in NYC

Cynthia Wang, Yihui Wang, Olivia Huang

May 2020

Where are the dogs in New York City? What are peoples preferences of dogs? How are people naming their dogs?
This project aims to answer these questions through various visualizations.

Lets locate the dogs!

Across boroughs

The overall distribution of dogs across boroughs didnt change much during 2014-2018. Compared to other boroughs, the number of dogs increased in Queens and Brooklyn in 2017 and 2018. While the number of dogs is consistently highest in Manhattan, it is the lowest in Staten Island.

By Zip Code

The map shows us the distribution of dogs over different Zip Codes and the most popular breed(s) in that region. Check out the dogs in your neighborhood!
